nodes.text: KOTOR Campaign Guide Web Enhancement 8: The Last Resort and the Moomo Williwaw

KOTOR Campaign Guide Web Enhancement 8 : The Last Resort and the Moomo Williwaw is an online supplement for Star Wars Roleplaying Game. It was published on the Wizards of the Coast website on November 14, 2008 and is a eigth in the series of web enhancements, which present material that didn't made it into Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide because of space reasons. This article covers the ships The Last Resort and the Moomo Williwaw.
